Meanwhile, Ankara Governor Erdogan Sahinoglu said at his
meeting with He Luli that he witnessed great changes in
China's economic construction in recent years during his visit
to China last year.
</P>
<P>
Sahinoglu expressed the hope that the cities of Ankara and
Beijing increase their ties in a bid to promote the relations
between Turkey and China.
</P>
<P>
He Luli arrived here on July 2 for a eight-day visit to
Turkey at the invitation of the government of Ankara
Municipality. 
