<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, July 4 (Xinhua) -- The Ethiopian parliament, the
House of People's Representatives, today approved a 9.57 billion
birr (6.35 birr equal one US dollar) budget for federal
government services in the new fiscal year beginning July 8.
</P>
<P>
Out of the total budget, 3.5 billion birr was appropriated for
