it would undermine the very nature of the articles in the
constitution.
</P>
<P>
The parliamentary committee which sat yesterday to vet the
ministerial appointment could not come out with results because
some nominees' curriculum vitae were not available, according
to the speaker.
</P>
<P>
The committtee is scheduled to sit this afternoon to continue
its work. 
