the Asian-Pacific region and the world at large, China's foreign
policy and domestic situation, defense policy and army building,
and also on the relations between the Chinese and Polish armies.
</P>
<P>
There exists traditional friendly ties between the two
countries, and their bilateral relations have enjoyed sustained
and steady development over recent years. Exchanges between two
armies are also on the rise.
</P>
<P>
Dobrzanski said there is great potential for cooperation
between the two armies, adding that he hopes the two sides will
work together to promote it.
</P>
<P>
The Polish Defense Minister also briefed Chi on regional
security and the Polish army's reforms.
</P>
<P>
After the talks, Chi held a dinner in honor of Dobrzanski, who
arrived here early this afternoon along with his party for a
seven-day visit at Chi's invitation. 
