rose by 40 cents to 14.9 Singapore dollars. The Development Bank
of Singapore (DBS) Foreign and the Overseas Chinese Banking
Corporation (OCBC) Foreign picked up by 30 cents each to finish at
17.1 and 16.9 Singapore dollars respectively. F&AMP;N gained by 20
cents to 14.7 Singapore dollars.
