<HEADLINE> Nanjing's Picture Show on Hong Kong's Return </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NANJING, July 5 (Xinhua) -- A picture speaks a thousand words,
the saying goes. And a photograph show in Nanjing is charting Hong
Kong's return to Chinese sovereignty.
</P>
<P>
A picture show, entitled "Greeting Hong Kong's Return to
Motherland", opened today in the capital city of east China's
Jiangsu Province.
</P>
<P>
The six-day show is sponsored by the Office of Hong Kong and
Macao Affairs under the State Council, the Hong Kong branch of the
Xinhua News Agency, the Hong Kong-based "Economic Herald",
Propaganda Department of the Jiangsu Provincial Committee of the
Communist Party of China, and the press office of the provincial
government.
</P>
