The show is divided into six sections, namely the Sino-British
talks on the future of Hong Kong, the signing of the "Sino-British
Joint Declaration", the birth of the Hong Kong Basic Law, Chinese
government ensuring the smooth transfer of Hong Kong, deep
affection between compatriots of China's inland areas and Hong
Kong, and a better tomorrow for Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
More than 200 pictures are on display. 
