<HEADLINE> Liaoning Seeks Foreign Cooperation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DALIAN, July 5 (Xinhua) -- Northeast China's Liaoning province
is actively seeking foreign economic and technical cooperation to
boost its economy.
</P>
<P>
